    <img src="/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/ChatGPT-Image-Nov-7-2025-11_59_17-PM.png" alt="Real Estate Team: The 7 People Every Scaling Investor Needs On Speed Dial" width="1200" height="675" loading="eager" />
  </figure>

